Creativity has always been at the core of everything I do.
With a degree in Art, I developed a deep appreciation for design, problem-solving, and

After moving to the U.S., I immersed myself in Full-Stack Development. However, it was iOS

I love bringing ideas to life, and I want to help people through technology, using my skills to
create better user experiences that look, feel, and function beautifully.
About
Smart assistant for cancer
treatment planning.
Provider App is an AI-powered medical assistant designed to help
doctors streamline cancer treatment planning while ensuring
compliance with hospital security protocols and industry
standards.
The app integrates with the Redox API to securely retrieve patient
data using name, last name, and birthdate, ensuring full
compliance with HIPAA (Health Insurance Portability and
Accountability Act), Insurance Portability and Accountability
Act) and FHIR (Fast Healthcare Interoperability Resources)
standards. It automatically verifies the patient records against
hospital certification guidelines before adding them to the
doctor’s patient list.

AI-powered treatment recommendations with
future pathway outcome predictions
Uses AI to analyze recent imaging scans &

Directly generate imaging reports

About
OncoPilot is an AI-driven physician decision support system,
starting with oncology. It combines trustworthy, agentic research
models with voice-driven interaction.
The app is designed to assist medical students and clinicians in
understanding cancer treatment recommendations.
Users can perform treatment calculations, discuss patient cases
through an AI chat, and generate accurate treatment plans—all while
ensuring patient data privacy.
